---
// Geteilte FAQ-Seite (alle Sprachen). Markup + Schema EINMAL; Inhalt je Locale aus
// site/i18n/content/faq.ts. DE-Route rendert dies mit lang="de" → Ausgabe identisch.
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { ORIGIN } from "../../lib/site";
import { breadcrumbLd, homeCrumb } from "../../lib/schema";
import { DEFAULT_LOCALE, localizedPath, type Locale } from "../../i18n";
import { faqMeta, faqItems } from "../../i18n/content/faq";

interface Props {
  lang?: Locale;
}
const { lang = DEFAULT_LOCALE } = Astro.props;

const meta = faqMeta[lang];
const faqs = faqItems[lang];

const faqUrl = `${ORIGIN}${localizedPath("/faq", lang)}`;
const faqSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  // Eigene @id/url, damit die volle /faq-Seite nicht mit dem Home-FAQ-Auszug kollidiert.
  "@id": `${faqUrl}#faq`,
  url: faqUrl,
  mainEntity: faqs.map((f) => ({
    "@type": "Question",
    name: f.q,
    acceptedAnswer: { "@type": "Answer", text: f.a },
  })),
};
const breadcrumb = breadcrumbLd(ORIGIN, lang, [homeCrumb(lang), { name: meta.heading, path: "/faq" }]);
---

<Layout
  title={meta.title}
  description={meta.description}
  canonicalPath={localizedPath("/faq", lang)}
  lang={lang}
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" slot="head" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" slot="head" set:html={JSON.stringify(breadcrumb)} />

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-muted/15 via-background to-muted/15">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-14 md:mb-20">
        <p class="eyebrow">{meta.eyebrow}</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mt-4 text-balance leading-[1.05]">
          {meta.heading}
        </h1>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-5 leading-relaxed text-pretty">
          {meta.intro}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-border/70">
        {faqs.map((f, i) => (
          <details class="faq-item border-b border-border/70" open={i === 0}>
            <summary class="flex items-start justify-between gap-5 py-6 md:py-7 cursor-pointer list-none group">
              <span class="font-display text-lg md:text-xl leading-snug text-balance pt-0.5 group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors">
                {f.q}
              </span>
              <svg class="faq-chevron shrink-0 mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 text-secondary transition-transform duration-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="pb-2 pr-8 md:pr-10 text-foreground/85 leading-relaxed max-w-prose">{f.a}</p>
            {f.links && f.links.length > 0 && (
              <p class="pb-7 pr-8 md:pr-10 flex flex-wrap gap-x-5 gap-y-1.5 text-sm">
                {f.links.map((l) => (
                  <a href={localizedPath(l.path, lang)} class="text-secondary underline underline-offset-4 hover:no-underline">{l.label}</a>
                ))}
              </p>
            )}
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Nativer Marker weg (Dreieck), eigener Chevron rotiert beim Öffnen. */
    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .faq-item[open] .faq-chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }
  </style>
</Layout>
